    {
      "instruction": "<p>Preheat the oven to 180&deg;C/ 160&deg;C (fan)/ 350&deg;F/ Gas 4</p>\r\n<p>Boil a kettle</p>\r\n<p>Peel and grate the <strong>brown</strong>&nbsp;<strong>onion<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span></strong></p>",
      "order": 1,
      "media": {
