          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>beef mixture</strong> to a baking tray (use <span class=\"text-highlight\"><strong>tin foil</strong></span> to avoid mess!) and shape into 1&nbsp;<span class=\"text-danger\">[2]</span> loaf<span class=\"text-danger\">[ves]</span></p>\r\n<p>Spread the <span class=\"text-highlight\"><strong>tomato</strong></span>&nbsp;<strong>ketchup</strong> over the top and put the tray in the oven for 30-35 min or until cooked through</p>",
